    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended primarily for those looking for a project car or a source for parts. While the frame remains intact, the engine requires significant repairs to become roadworthy again, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. The exterior has several large dents and peeling clear coat, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest time and resources into mechanical restoration if you intend to use this as a daily driver.",
