    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is very sound; the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it ready for daily driving. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear, such as small surface scratches or light upholstery fading, there are no major defects or necessary repairs. Potential buyers can expect a reliable, comfortable ride that has many miles of service left to offer.",
      "price": 34500.0,
